messages.message: Just closing the loop here... the final recommendation, after much convo and consideration (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05NKL85Y2G/p1706034775854889?thread_ts=1705967218.593949&cid=C05NKL85Y2G), is to change *Single Field* to *Text*.
